{"type":"message","id":"08ff904b","parentId":"a24e8f83","timestamp":"2026-05-20T01:00:00.153Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:rules-refresh-daily Cursor协作规则刷新] 【每日规则刷新】请记住以下 Cursor 协作规则（每天提醒一次）：\n\n1. 当用户要求让 Cursor 做某件事时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --title \"任务标题\" --instructions \"具体指令\" --submitted-by \"OpenClaw\" --notify\n\n2. 当用户回复了 Cursor 发来的飞书确认消息时，必须执行：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\confirm_write.py\" --task-id \"task_id\" --decision auto --reply \"用户回复原文\"\n\n3. 查看当前 Cursor 任务队列：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --list\n\n4. 查看已完成任务结果：\npython \"C:\\ADHD_agent\\.cursor\\skills\\async-notify\\scripts\\submit_task.py\" --results\n\n以上规则已写入 AGENTS.md，请确认记住。无需回复，静默确认即可。\nCurrent time: Wednesday, May 20th, 2026 — 09:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-05-20 01:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1779238800150}}
{"type":"message","id":"21a22f9b","parentId":"08ff904b","timestamp":"2026-05-20T01:02:54.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job reminder about Cursor collaboration rules. The user wants me to silently confirm and remember these rules. I don't need to respond visibly - just acknowledge internally and confirm the rules are noted."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n已确认记住 Cursor 协作规则，将在用户触发对应场景时执行相应脚本：\n1. 用户要求 Cursor 做事 → submit_task.py --notify\n2. 用户回复 Cursor 确认消息 → confirm_write.py --decision auto\n3. 查看任务队列 → submit_task.py --list\n4. 查看已完成结果 → submit_task.py --results\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779238800152}}
